      "updated": 1267628400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec27aff09e00003d4b7f",
      "text": " <<",
      "created": 1267628400,
      "updated": 1267628400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec27aff09e00003d4b80",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1267628400,
      "updated": 1267628400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec27aff09e00003d4b81",
      "text": " 心が痛い…。ドキュメントを書いていないせいで放置され朽ち果てたプロジェクトがいくつあることやら…。懇親会でも「GRINEditってどうなった？」って聞かれたし。",
      "created": 1267628400,
      "updated": 1267628400,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec27aff09e00003d4b82",
      "text": " ",
